Abuja (Sundiata Post) – Annie Idibia the wife of iconic singer, 2face Idibia has revealed that her husband is ill. According to Annie, the singer is down and has been placed on drip. She added that despite his ill state, he still managed to pull himself up to attend a work event. “Incredible human!! So Baba has been so ill n on drips n plenty meds! Dr was by his side for 48hrs! We all didn’t think he could make it to this big event that was all about him and the Nigeria stock exchange.” Read the rest of her post below; Culled from Information Nigeria